MLP Aware Cost-Benefit Analysis of Cache Replacements

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

requestEvicter, request, requestVictim

replacementTimestamp := infinity
nextUseTimestamp := infinity
victimNextUseTimestamp := infinity

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 

for any miss (request) to any cache with any replacement policy: 

(1) replacementTimestamp < nextUseTimestamp < victimNextUseTimestamp => useless: fill -> evicted
baseline (bypass): replacementTimestamp < victimNextUseTimestamp => victim miss; request miss
result: victim miss; request miss
delta(misses) = 0
delta(missCosts) = 0

(2) replacementTimestamp < victimNextUseTimestamp < nextUseTimestamp => useless: fill -> evicted
baseline (bypass): replacementTimestamp < victimNextUseTimestamp => victim miss; request miss 
result: victim miss; request miss
delta(misses) = 0
delta(missCosts) = 0

(3) nextUseTimestamp < replacementTimestamp < victimNextUseTimestamp => good: fill -> hits++ -> evicted
baseline (bypass): replacementTimestamp < victimNextUseTimestamp => victim miss; request miss
result: victim miss; request hit
delta(misses) = -1
delta(missCosts) = -requestMissCost

(4) victimNextUseTimestamp < replacementTimestamp < nextUseTimestamp => bad: fill -> miss++ -> evicted
baseline (bypass): victimNextUseTimestamp < replacementTimestamp => victim hit; request miss
result: victim miss; request miss
delta(misses) = +1
delta(missCosts) = +victimMissCost

(5) nextUseTimestamp < victimNextUseTimestamp < replacementTimestamp => ugly?: fill -> hits++, miss++ -> evicted
baseline (bypass): victimNextUseTimestamp < replacementTimestamp => victim hit; request miss
result: victim miss; request hit
delta(misses) = (+1) + (-1)
delta(missCosts) = (+victimMissCost) + (-requestMissCost) = victimMissCost - requestMissCost

(6) victimNextUseTimestamp < nextUseTimestamp < replacementTimestamp => ugly?: fill -> miss++, hit++ -> evicted
baseline (bypass): victimNextUseTimestamp < replacementTimestamp => victim hit; request miss
result: victim miss; request hit
delta(misses) = (+1) + (-1)
delta(misses) = (+victimMissCost) + (-requestMissCost) = victimMissCost - requestMissCost
